Note: ============================================================================
Note: Kotlin Lexer - Tokenization for Kotlin Language
Note: Part of Translation Universal Translation System
Note: Kotlin -> HIR Frontend (Android Standard Language)
Note: ============================================================================

Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/core/string_core.runa" as StringCore
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/memory/layout.runa" as Layout

